    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "fourteen minutes, Pierman saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "bright lights that resemble",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "shooting stars, but three of them",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "moving horizontally, unlike any shoot-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "ing star he had ever seen. Another com-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "mercial pilot who was reached in flight",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "nearby said that he saw a light off his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "left wing; Barnes found a corresponding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "pip on the radarscope. Other pilots in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "vicinity reported, however, that they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "could see nothing unusual. Toward",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "daybreak, ten peculiar pips were counted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "simultaneously on Barnes' screen.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "\"There is no other conclusion I can",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "reach but that for six hours on the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "morning of the twentieth of July there",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "were at least ten unidentifiable objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "moving above Washington,\" Barnes",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "wrote. \"They were not ordinary air-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "craft. . . . Nor in my opinion could any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "natural phenomena account for these",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "spots on our radar. Neither shooting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "stars, electrical disturbances, nor clouds",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "could, either. Exactly what they are, I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "don't know. Now you know as much",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "about them as I do. And your guess is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "as good as mine.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "A week later, at 9:08 P.M. on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "July 26th, the Air Route Traffic Con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "trol Center's radarscope again showed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "unidentifiable objects over Washing-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "ton. So did the screen at the Andrews",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "Air Force Base, just outside the capi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "tal. Two jet interceptors, capable of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "doing six hundred miles an hour,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "were dispatched from a base near New",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "Castle, Delaware, to investigate. When",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "the interceptors appeared on the radar-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "scopes, they were guided toward the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "objects. One of the pilots sighted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "four lights approximately ten miles",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "in front of his plane and slightly above",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "it, but they vanished while he was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "trying to overtake them. Twenty",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "minutes later, he saw \"a steady white",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "light,\" but within a minute it, too,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "disappeared. \"We have no evidence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "they were flying saucers,\" an Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "representative said later. \"Conversely,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "we have no evidence they were not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "flying saucers. We don't know what",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "they were.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "As a result of these two incidents,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "particularly the one involving the inter-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "ceptors, public agitation reached a new",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "height. The Air Force was bombarded",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "with hundreds of letters, telephone calls,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "and telegrams demanding information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "and offering advice. One of the smaller",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "airlines supplied its crews with cameras",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "and ordered them to photograph any",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "saucers they encountered. A civilian",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "wrote to the Air Force that he would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "let it in on \"the secret\" in return for a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "colonelcy. A Los Angeles pastor wrote",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "to Einstein, beseeching him to clear up",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
